author: kirotv.com
title: Barn fire breaks out in Lacey
text:
Firefighters battled flames at a large barn in Lacey early Monday.
A man was inside the barn in the 11000 block of Evergreen Valley Road Southeast when the fire started but he was able to get out safely.
No people were hurt and no animals were inside the barn when the fire started.
The barn fire was out by about 5:50 a.m.
